--- !u!114 &697990567
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 697990562}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 28e85389ca13cb34c9d7a32ffdf6c81e, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::dialogueInfo
  herSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aa2416d8a520fee4590182df4194d379, type: 3}
  himSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0af74699b57c5d14aae5c63598ff9ce2, type: 3}
  teacherSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 849d784e8a0260a48840818e1b0ad8c8, type: 3}
  npcSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 47d3254be5bf5e04e9cf8d5ae57941dc, type: 3}
  voidSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: db0f97e31094b96499a1b217a79d0e82, type: 3}
  HerOpening1:
  - Huh? Where am I.....What happened?
  - This place is dark......Hello???...................................Hellooooooooooooooooo???
  - Am I all alone here?
  VoidOpening1:
  - Wow...you really came...I never thought I'd see the day you finally came back
    here.
  - After all, it's been quite a while since you've given this place any thought...
  HerOpening2:
  - Huh? What is that supposed to mean? Where am I? And who are you?
  VoidOpening2:
  - If you've forgotten who I am then we really do have a problem. And I'm surprised
    you don't even recognize your own mind.
  - But then again, you haven't been yourself for quite a while, who am I to expect
    you to remember?
  - But anyway, welcome back. I wish the place were in a better state for you, but
    that's not necessarily under my control, you carry all the power now.
  HerOpening3:
  - Wait what? This is my mind? How did I get here....the last thing I remember I
    was in the church in my wedding dress and now...I'm here...
  - But now that I think about it...I can't remember past that. Why was I getting
    married? And to whom? How did I even get here?! I feel like I don't even know
    myself anymore...
  - And if this is my mind...why is it so dark and disheveled? I don't want to live
    like this...How do I fix it?
  VoidOpening3:
  - Wow it really is worse than I thought huh...you can't remember ANYTHING?
  - This place has been falling apart at the seams for ages but recently it's been
    dissapearing at a faster rate. The whole place is bound to cave in soon.
  - It seems you've lost sight of who you are, and it seems this decision you are
    making is the cause of it.
  - 'There''s a way out of this, but to do that you need to remember who you are. '
  - This is your last chance. Otherwise I'm assuming this place will shut down for
    good, and you, me, and everything you have left here will go with it.
  HerOpening4:
  - Wait what? This is all happening so fast? How do I even start?
  VoidOpening4:
  - To remember who you are, we have to go backwards. Let's start with where you
    are now. Your adulthood.
  - Find the open door and enter it to start.
  introAdulthood:
  - woah it empty in here
  - what i jump
  - '*watches*'
  - nawwww
  adulthoodEnd:
  - naw man get me outta this booty ass bitch
  - like NEOW
